    <apiVersion>66.0</apiVersion>
    <description>When a Template_Version__c transitions to Status=Approved, invoke TemplateVersionApprovalHandler to stamp Approved_At__c on every related Template_Mapping__c that doesn't already carry a stamp. Idempotent.</description>
